  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We led Dallas but failed - Mahinda action",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "We have paid attention to the government to be established. Whatever government is formed should serve the people of the country. Former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa said that he will act according to the decisions taken by the party.",
        "He mentioned the above in a comment to the media after the vote for the election of the President was held in the Parliament today on Wednesday 20th.",
        "We are observing about the government being established. Whatever form the government takes, it must serve the people. A lot can be achieved if the basic problems are solved.",
        "No party-wise decisions have been taken so far regarding the government led by President Ranil Wickremesinghe. I will act according to the decisions taken by the party.",
        "We featured and voted for former Minister Dulles Alagaperuma but she lost the race. This is common in politics. One will win the competition and the other will lose.",
        "There are two different opinions regarding the appointment of President Ranil Wickremesinghe. However, he said that in the current situation, attention should be paid to solving the basic problems."
      ],
